on functions and 1D and 2D transfer functions, we find\nthat the rotating outflow model is compatible with observations of the BLR in\nNGC 5548.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 1996 15:45:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-28"}
